title: 01/19/21  DPS Hour 3 Jeff Passan and Chris Webber

description:
Jeff Passan talks to Dan about the Mets GM being fired for sexting a reporter in 2016. Chris Webber tells Dan that Steve Nash is the perfect coach for James Harden. Chris says that Steve Nash dribbled the ball a lot too.
